************************************************************
STJERM:

* version SVN
* a terminal emulator which shows up and hides by pressing the
  shortcut key
* by Stjepan Glavina

************************************************************
REQUIREMENTS:

* mono
* gtk-sharp-2
* vte

************************************************************
INSTALLATION:

Compile:
    ./compile
Install (as root):
    ./install

************************************************************
KNOWN BUGS:

No known bugs at the moment.
If you find any, please report them to stjepang AT gmail DOT com.

************************************************************
CHANGELOG:

0.1:
    * date: SVN
    * initial release
